"title": "6214: participation, in Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6214",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The joining of believers to Jesus Christ, through faith, whereby they are freed from participation in Adam by sharing in Christ's death and resurrection, his nature, sufferings and glory and whereby, too, they become part of his body. Believers therefore share in the fellowship, ministry and hope of God's people, which is anticipated by the OT and fulfilled in the church.</p>\n<h2>Believers are united with Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:8\">JHN 13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:17\">1CO 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:14\">HEB 3:14</a></p>\n<h2>Faith liberates from participation in sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15\">ROM 5:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:16-Rom5:21\">ROM 5:16–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:21-1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:21–15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:11\">COL 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Participation in Christ</h2>\n<h3>In Christ's death and resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:3-Rom6:4\">ROM 6:3–6:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:5-Rom6:8\">ROM 6:5–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4\">ROM 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:27\">GAL 3:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12-Col2:13\">COL 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:11\">2TI 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>In Christ's nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2CO 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:10\">COL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:10\">HEB 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>In Christ's sufferings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:5\">2CO 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>In Christ's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:22\">JHN 17:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:6\">EPH 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:14\">2TH 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:12\">2TI 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Participation in Christ's body</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:16-1Cor10:17\">1CO 10:16–10:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:5\">ROM 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27\">1CO 12:27</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing unity through Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:28\">GAL 3:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1CO 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:21–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:11\">COL 3:11</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing a source of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:16\">EPH 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4-John15:5\">JHN 15:4–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17\">ROM 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:19\">COL 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing an inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:29\">GAL 3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:19\">1SA 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:5\">PSA 106:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:25\">ACT 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:32\">ACT 20:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:17\">HEB 6:17</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing spiritual blessings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3\">EPH 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:27\">ROM 15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7\">PHP 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4\">HEB 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing a hope</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:35\">LUK 20:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing in worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26\">1CO 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:12-2Chr5:13\">2CH 5:12–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:24\">NEH 12:24</a></p>\n<h3>Accepting responsibility towards others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:26\">1CO 12:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1-Gal6:2\">GAL 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:4\">PHP 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing one another's sufferings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14\">PHP 4:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:33-Heb10:34\">HEB 10:33–10:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9\">REV 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing with those in need</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:16\">EZK 45:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:4\">2CO 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:13\">2CO 9:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:16\">HEB 13:16</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing in God's work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:1\">2CO 6:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:5\">PHP 1:5</a></strong> <em>Paul thanks the Philippians for their active support of his ministry.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:24\">NUM 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:2\">NUM 18:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:38\">1CH 16:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:2\">EZR 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:10-1Cor9:13\">1CO 9:10–9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:20\">2CO 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:7-Gal2:9\">GAL 2:7–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:15-Phil4:16\">PHP 4:15–4:16</a></p>\n<h2>Participation in Christ demands holiness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:21\">1CO 10:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:15\">1CO 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6-Eph5:7\">EPH 5:6–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:5\">COL 3:1–3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Participation of the nations in God's salvation</h2>\n<h3>Gentiles are included among God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">EPH 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:24\">ROM 11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:8-Gal3:9\">GAL 3:8–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:3\">GEN 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:18\">GEN 18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:18\">GEN 22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:14\">GAL 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>God's promise to include the nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:11\">ZEC 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:3\">ISA 2:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:2\">MIC 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:1\">ISA 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:23-Isa19:25\">ISA 19:23–19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:11\">ZEP 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16\">ZEC 14:16</a></p>",
